</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fertilisation_of_Orchids_1877_edition_title_page.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Book title page containing &quot;THE VARIOUS CONTRIVANCES BY WHICH ORCHIDS ARE FERTILISED BY INSECTS. By CHARLES DARWIN, M.A., F.R.S., &amp;c. SECOND EDITION, REVISED. WITH ILLUSTRATIONS. NEW YORK: D. APPLETON AND COMPANY, 549 AND 551 BROADWAY. 1877." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/Fertilisation_of_Orchids_1877_edition_title_page.jpg/200px-Fertilisation_of_Orchids_1877_edition_title_page.jpg" width="200" height="331" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/Fertilisation_of_Orchids_1877_edition_title_page.jpg/300px-Fertilisation_of_Orchids_1877_edition_title_page.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/Fertilisation_of_Orchids_1877_edition_title_page.jpg/400px-Fertilisation_of_Orchids_1877_edition_title_page.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
